ZH: 我家有十头牲畜。
EN: There are ten head of livestock on my farm.

ZH: 牲畜是农民们的主要财产。
EN: Livestock are the main asset for farmers.

ZH: 这些牲畜都很健康。
EN: These livestock are all very healthy.

ZH: 农民们每天都要喂牲畜。
EN: Farmers have to feed the livestock every day.

ZH: 牲畜需要足够的水和食物。
EN: Livestock need plenty of water and food.

ZH: 他养了很多种不同的牲畜。
EN: He raises many different kinds of livestock.

ZH: 畜牧业是一个重要的经济产业。
EN: Animal husbandry is an important economic industry.

ZH: 这里的牲畜都是放养的。
EN: The livestock here are all raised in pasture.

ZH: 牲畜养殖是一种传统工作。
EN: Livestock breeding is a traditional occupation.

ZH: 每个牲畜都有自己的编号。
EN: Each livestock has its own identification number.

ZH: 牲畜运输要保证安全和舒适。
EN: Livestock transportation must be safe and comfortable.

ZH: 这些牲畜的品种很多。
EN: There are many different breeds of livestock.

ZH: 老农民懂得如何照顾牲畜。
EN: Old farmers know how to take care of livestock.

ZH: 牲畜需要被定期检查。
EN: Livestock need to be checked regularly.

ZH: 在牲畜市场上有很多买卖。
EN: There is a lot of buying and selling at the livestock market.

ZH: 牲畜疾病会给农民带来损失。
EN: Livestock diseases can cause losses for farmers.

ZH: 牲畜肉是人们的主要食物来源之一。
EN: Livestock meat is one of the main sources of food for people.

ZH: 牲畜草场需要进行定期修剪。
EN: Livestock pastures need to be regularly trimmed.

ZH. 这位农夫用心照料他的牲畜。
EN: This farmer takes good care of his livestock.

ZH: 牲畜的生长需要一定的时间。
EN: The growth of livestock takes a certain amount of time.
